<https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/53000973/2025-26/evaluation> a ns1:EvaluationSystem ;
    ns1:evaluationDescription """-Complete work: includes all requested results
-Depth of work performed: criteria considered, arguments made
-Checks performed to verify the correct functioning of the models
-Number of references made to other works
-Structure and quality of the presentation
-Number of design optimization iterations performed
-Consideration of other design criteria (economic, manufacturing, environmental, assembly, transportation, recycling, aesthetics, etc.)"""@es .

